    <item>
      <title>美元走强、英伟达前景不乐观 新兴市场受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/strong-dollar-nvidia-suspense-keep-emerging-markets-in-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美元近期的抛售幅度过大，大多数新兴市场货币周三均出现下跌。股票投资者等待当天晚些时候 Nvidia Inc. 的业绩来判断科技行业的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/strong-dollar-nvidia-suspense-keep-emerging-markets-in-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:31:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着拘留时间临近，法国正在考虑对 Telegram 首席执行官采取下一步行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/telegram-ceo-to-face-off-with-judge-when-four-day-detention-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[接下来的 24 小时将决定 Telegram 首席执行官帕维尔·杜罗夫 (Pavel Durov) 的命运，他因被控允许犯罪分子不受限制地使用该消息应用程序而在巴黎被拘留了四天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/telegram-ceo-to-face-off-with-judge-when-four-day-detention-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:29:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国敦促 Telegram 严厉打击 Deepfake 性犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/south-korea-urges-telegram-to-crack-down-on-deepfake-sex-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于此类内容激增，韩国政府已要求通讯应用程序 Telegram 和其他社交媒体公司从其平台上删除露骨的深度伪造性爱图片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/south-korea-urges-telegram-to-crack-down-on-deepfake-sex-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:54:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
